; This regression test verifies that lines longer than 4096 characters can be
; parsed successfully (GitHub issue #1149).  The comment line below is 5000+
; characters, well beyond the old 4096-byte limit.
;
; 

2016/01/01 Income
    assets:cash  $1
    income

test bal
                  $1  assets:cash
                 $-1  income
--------------------
                   0
end test
